cs.SI, cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.SD, cs.DS 

This paper discusses a preprocessing algorithm for Twitter data stream classification, which involves natural language processing and data mining techniques. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-categories of Social and Information Networks (cs.SI), Computation and Language (cs.CL), Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Software Engineering (cs.SE), and Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS). However, since the focus is on sentiment analysis and classification, cs.SI and cs.CL are the most likely sub-categories.
